					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Yes, I guess you could modify any TKROM and TSROM board easily to have TLSROM like mirroring. As you said, connect CIRAM A10 (on the cart edge) on CHR A16 (MMC3) instead of normal CIRAM A10 (MMC3) pin. Also make sure your hack work with mapper 118 before doing that.</div>

